OL,3,CHistoric rail vehicles assembled for
OL,4,C'Europe's biggest display'
OL,6,FDozens of rail vehicles have been
OL,7,Fassembled at a museum in County Durham
OL,8,Ffor what curators claim will be the
OL,9,Fbiggest display of its kind in Europe.
OL,11,FLocomotion announced it has completed
OL,12,Fthe movement of 46 vehicles into a new
OL,13,F#8 million New Hall building at its
OL,14,Fsite in Shildon.
OL,16,FThese include steam locomotives, hand-
OL,17,Fpowered track inspection machines,
OL,18,Ffreight wagons, snow ploughs and an
OL,19,Farmoured vehicle on tracks.
