OL,6,FFilling New Hall involved a complex
OL,7,Ffour-week operation.
OL,9,FCombined with what was already at
OL,10,FLocomotion, this brings the site's
OL,11,Ftotal number of vehicles to 99.
OL,13,FThe museum said that is more than any
OL,14,Fother indoor display in Europe.
OL,16,FLocomotion is built close to the site
OL,17,Fof Shildon Works, a thriving railway
OL,18,Fworkshop once employing thousands of
OL,19,Fpeople which closed in June 1984.
