OL,6,FSarah Price, head of the museum,
OL,7,Fdescribed its new building as
OL,8,F"magnificent".
OL,10,FShe said: "New Hall effectively
OL,11,Fdoubles the size of Locomotion and
OL,12,Fgives us much needed covered display
OL,13,Fspace to help conserve the collection,
OL,14,Fas well as giving visitors the chance
OL,15,Fto find out more about the railways
OL,16,Fand the North East's railway heritage.
