OL,6,F"We were delighted to be able to
OL,7,Fprovide funding for this project,
OL,8,Fwhich will let many more people know
OL,9,Fthe significance of Shildon as the
OL,10,Fstarting point of the world's first
OL,11,Fsteam locomotive-powered passenger
OL,12,Fjourney, further raising Durham's
OL,13,Fprofile nationally and internationally
OL,14,Fas the Culture County.
OL,16,F"Locomotion is already one of County
OL,17,FDurham and the North East's biggest
OL,18,Fvisitor attractions, putting smiles on
OL,19,Ffaces and delivering significant
OL,20,Feconomic benefits.
