OL,6,F"We look forward to New Hall adding to
OL,7,Fthe museum's offer and to it being at
OL,8,Fthe heart of celebrations of both 20
OL,9,Fyears of the museum and 200 years
OL,10,Fsince the opening of the Stockton and
OL,11,FDarlington Railway."
OL,13,FNew Hall will open to the public on
OL,14,FMay 24.
